amascus.`}]},{id:2,title:`Bright Light Road`,shortTitle:`The Bright Light`,icon:`sunburst`,storySummary:`A bright light from heaven stopped Paul on the road.`,questions:[{id:`light-1`,checkpointId:2,mode:`multiple-choice`,prompt:`What appeared around Saul on the road?`,choices:[{id:`light`,label:`A bright light`},{id:`river`,label:`A rushing river`},{id:`snow`,label:`Falling snow`}],correctChoiceId:`light`,explanation:`A bright light from heaven shone around Saul.`},{id:`light-2`,checkpointId:2,mode:`true-false`,prompt:`True or false: Saul heard Jesus speak to him.`,choices:[{id:`true`,label:`True`},{id:`false`,label:`False`}],correctChoiceId:`true`,explanation:`Jesus called Saul by name and spoke to him.`},{id:`light-3`,checkpointId:2,mode:`multiple-choice`,prompt:`What happened when Saul stood up?`,choices:[{id:`blind`,label:`He could not see`},{id:`flew`,label:`He began to fly`},{id:`ran`,label:`He won a race`}],correctChoiceId:`blind`,explanation:`Saul opened his eyes, but he could not see.`},{id:`light-4`,checkpointId:2,mode:`teacher-judged`,prompt:`How do you think Saul felt when the bright light appeared?`},{id:`light-5`,checkpointId:2,mode:`picture-choice`,prompt:`Which picture best matches what shone around Saul?`,choices:[{id:`sun`,label:`Bright light`,image:`☀️`},{id:`rain`,label:`Rain cloud`,image:`🌧️`},{id:`moon`,label:`Moon`,image:`🌙`}],correctChoiceId:`sun`,explanation:`A light from heaven shone all around him.`}]},{id:3,title:`Damascus House`,shortTitle:`Waiting in Damascus`,icon:`house`,storySummary:`Saul was led into Damascus, where he waited and prayed.`,questions:[{id:`city-1`,checkpointId:3,mode:`multiple-choice`,prompt:`Could Saul see when he entered Damascus?`,choices:[{id:`yes`,label:`Yes`},{id:`no`,label:`No`}],correctChoiceId:`no`,explanation:`Saul's companions led him by the hand because he could not see.`},{id:`city-2`,checkpointId:3,mode:`multiple-choice`,prompt:`Who helped Saul travel into the city?`,choices:[{id:`friends`,label:`His companions`},{id:`camel`,label:`A talking camel`},{id:`king`,label:`A king`}],correctChoiceId:`friends`,explanation:`The men traveling with Saul led him into Damascus.`},{id:`city-3`,checkpointId:3,mode:`true-false`,prompt:`True or false: Saul prayed while he waited.`,choices:[{id:`true`,label:`True`},{id:`false`,label:`False`}],correctChoiceId:`true`,explanation:`Saul spent the time praying.`},{id:`city-4`,checkpointId:3,mode:`teacher-judged`,prompt:`What can we do when we need God's help?`},{id:`city-5`,checkpointId:3,mode:`picture-choice`,prompt:`Which place did Saul enter?`,choices:[{id:`city`,label:`A city`,image:`🏘️`},{id:`ocean`,label:`The ocean`,image:`🌊`},{id:`mountain`,label:`A snowy mountain`,image:`🏔️`}],correctChoiceId:`city`,explanation:`Saul was led through the gate into Damascus.`}]},{id:4,title:`Good News Square`,shortTitle:`Paul Tells Others`,icon:`speaking-scroll`,storySummary:`Saul could see again, was baptized, and told others about Jesus.`,questions:[{id:`preach-1`,checkpointId:4,mode:`teacher-judged`,prompt:`Who did Saul tell people about?`},{id:`preach-2`,checkpointId:4,mode:`multiple-choice`,prompt:`Who came to visit and help Saul?`,choices:[{id:`ananias`,label:`Ananias`},{id:`david`,label:`David`},{id:`noah`,label:`Noah`}],correctChoiceId:`ananias`,explanation:`God sent Ananias to Saul.`},{id:`preach-3`,checkpointId:4,mode:`true-false`,prompt:`True or false: Saul could see again after Ananias prayed for him.`,choices:[{id:`true`,label:`True`},{id:`false`,label:`False`}],correctChoiceId:`true`,explanation:`Something like scales fell from Saul's eyes, and he could see.`},{id:`preach-4`,checkpointId:4,mode:`picture-choice`,prompt:`Which picture shows sharing good news?`,choices:[{id:`speak`,label:`Speaking to friends`,image:`🗣️`},{id:`sleep`,label:`Sleeping`,image:`😴`},{id:`hide`,label:`Hiding`,image:`🙈`}],correctChoiceId:`speak`,explanation:`Saul spoke boldly and shared the good news about Jesus.`},{id:`preach-5`,checkpointId:4,mode:`multiple-choice`,prompt:`What did Saul do after he could see again?`,choices:[{id:`shared`,label:`He told people about Jesus`},{id:`hid`,label:`He hid forever`},{id:`forgot`,label:`He forgot what happened`}],correctChoiceId:`shared`,explanation:`Saul's changed life became a story he shared with others.`}]},{id:5,title:`Story Summit`,shortTitle:`Whole Story Review`,icon:`map`,storySummary:`Put the whole Road to Damascus story together.`,questions:[{id:`overview-1`,checkpointId:5,mode:`multiple-choice`,prompt:`Where was Saul traveling when Jesus spoke to him?`,choices:[{id:`damascus`,label:`Damascus`},{id:`egypt`,label:`Egypt`},{id:`rome`,label:`Rome`}],correctChoiceId:`damascus`,explanation:`Jesus met Saul on the road to Damascus.`},{id:`overview-2`,checkpointId:5,mode:`multiple-choice`,prompt:`Put the first event in the story: what happened on the road?`,choices:[{id:`light`,label:`A bright light appeared`},{id:`preach`,label:`Saul preached in the city`},{id:`visit`,label:`Ananias visited`}],correctChoiceId:`light`,explanation:`The bright light and Jesus' voice began Saul's change.`},{id:`overview-3`,checkpointId:5,mode:`true-false`,prompt:`True or false: Meeting Jesus changed Saul's life.`,choices:[{id:`true`,label:`True`},{id:`false`,label:`False`}],correctChoiceId:`true`,explanation:`Saul went from stopping Jesus' followers to telling others about Jesus.`},{id:`overview-4`,checkpointId:5,mode:`teacher-judged`,prompt:`Tell one part of the Road to Damascus story in your own words.`},{id:`overview-5`,checkpointId:5,mode:`picture-choice`,prompt:`Which set of pictures tells our story?`,choices:[{id:`story`,label:`Light, prayer, good news`,image:`☀️ 🙏 📜`},{id:`weather`,label:`Snow, umbrella, boat`,image:`❄️ ☂️ ⛵`},{id:`food`,label:`Apple, bread, cake`,image:`🍎 🍞 🎂`}],correctChoiceId:`story`,explanation:`The light, Saul's prayer, and sharing good news help us remember the story.`}]}]}.checkpoints,f=new Map(d.flatMap(e=>e.questions).map(e=>[e.id,e]));function p(e){return d.find(t=